## Project Overview

CollegeCBT is a SvelteKit + Tailwind CSS enterprise exam-preparation platform for Nigerian students, integrating AI question generation via Claude API, Firebase Auth, and Cloudflare Pages edge deployment.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| Framework | SvelteKit 2.x (TypeScript) |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS + Custom CSS Variables |
| Auth | Firebase Auth (client-side only, lazy-loaded) |
| AI | Claude 3.5 Haiku via Anthropic API |
| Deployment | Cloudflare Pages (adapter-cloudflare) |
| Fonts | DM Serif Display, DM Sans, JetBrains Mono, Bebas Neue |

